{"tid":2462982,"cid":21,"subCid":4,"title":"[K-indie] 一人一個韓國非主流音樂分享","createTime":"2021-03-26T10:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T11:07:50.000Z","uid":392530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3525ada5b78900a31cab43b9ac13b11d293525ae","tid":2462982,"uid":392530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"本來睇緊EXO(好似)嗰陣，畀Youtube演算法帶咗去聽J_ust，先發現原來好多韓國Indie都勁好聽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過聽咗J_ust之後，個演算法只係不停帶我聽我稱之為「韓國Cafe」歌嘅音樂。唔知大家平時有冇聽開咩K-Indie推介吓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係幾首我覺得J_ust好好聽嘅歌：<br />\n<br />\nJ_ust(그_냥) -  I want to be a pillow (베개가 되고 싶어요)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ai7J5HCLC8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4ai7J5HCLC8&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=396a4598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4ai7J5HCLC8</a> <br />\n<br />\nJ_ust (그_냥) - Goodbye (안녕)&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pi-YiWrezJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPi-YiWrezJA&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=9e2f6d8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pi-YiWrezJA</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;同場加映宣傳&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n其實小弟平時都有填吓詞嘅習慣，鐘意搵啲日韓歌嚟填，之前都填咗兩首J_ust，送埋畀大家聽吓。<br />\n<br />\nI want to be a pillow嘅廣東話版<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sEvKwzN0Qas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsEvKwzN0Qas&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=2eeb84ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sEvKwzN0Qas</a> <br />\n<br />\n改至J_ust另一首叫Way Back Home嘅歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xLAsN74sQQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxLAsN74sQQw&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ac6bb9ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xLAsN74sQQw</a><br />\n<br />\n我仲有填其他歌，可以去另一個集合Post睇。歡迎大家推介吓其他韓國音樂畀我填。<br />\n<br />\n［借曲填詞］練詞庵--逢星期4分享，自填自唱--<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2413152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2413152</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b93ad44dfee8e55ccdb7a04cb1d42b346689604","tid":2462982,"uid":256790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:07:50.000Z","msg":"好鍾意呢隊band 叫dasutt <br />\n唔知稱唔稱得上indie <br />\n不過K indie心目中係得佢地同hyukoh 永遠超越唔到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EyaSPPO4Ny8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEyaSPPO4Ny8&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=d68ec482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EyaSPPO4Ny8</a><br />\n<br />\nLike a sea<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/641IA7jiz4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F641IA7jiz4Y&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=b1b3147a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/641IA7jiz4Y</a><br />\n<br />\nYouth"}]}